                                title="Office of the Historical Advisor (1929–1933)">HA</abbr>)</li>
                        <li>1931–1933, Hunter Miller (<abbr
                                title="Office of the Historical Advisor (1929–1933)">HA</abbr>)</li>
                        <li>1933–1939, Cyril Wynne (<abbr
                                title="Division of Research and Publications (1933–1946)"
                            >RP</abbr>)</li>
                        <li>1939–1946, E. Wilder Spaulding (<abbr
                                title="Division of Research and Publications (1933–1946)"
                            >RP</abbr>)</li>
                        <li>1946–1962, George Bernard Noble (<abbr
